8 AS INTRODUCED
9 A Concurrent Resolution authorizing the Oklahoma
House of Representatives or the Oklahoma State Senate
10 to amend or modify legislative deadlines applicable
to the 2nd Session of the 60th Oklahoma Legislature
11 pursuant to Joint Rule 7(c).
12
13
14 WHEREAS, pursuant to Rule 7(c) of the Joint Rules of the
15 Oklahoma House of Representatives and the Oklahoma State Senate, the
16 legislative schedule may be amended or modified by the adoption of a
17 concurrent resolution by a majority vote of the membership of each
18 chamber; and
19 WHEREAS, based on the provisions set forth in Rule 7(c) of the
20 Joint Rules, the legislative schedule previously adopted by the
21 Oklahoma House of Representatives and the Oklahoma State Senate
22 shall be set aside for the remainder of the 2nd Session of the 60th
23 Oklahoma Legislature.
