1 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES
2 OF THE 2ND SESSION OF THE 60TH OKLAHOMA LEGISLATURE, THE SENATE
3 CONCURRING THEREIN:
4 THAT pursuant to 7(c) of the Joint Rules of the Oklahoma House
5 of Representatives and the Oklahoma State Senate, the legislative
6 schedule previously adopted by the Oklahoma House of Representatives
7 and the Oklahoma State Senate shall, on this date, Wednesday, May 6,
8 2026, be set aside for the remainder of the 2nd Session of the 60th
9 Oklahoma Legislature.
10
11 DIRECT TO CALENDAR.
